These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, blues, funk, indie
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
3. the fan of funk is between the fan of blues and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Music-Genre      | indie | house | funk   | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, teacher, paramedic, firefighter
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the paramedic and the colombian##2
2. the firefighter is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | teacher | electrician | paramedic | firefighter |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, folk, rock, reggae
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the fan of rock is between the fan of folk and the person eating corn##2
3. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
4. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating corn is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock   | reggae | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, november, october
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who's birthday is in september and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Birthday   | november | october | september | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, monopoly, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Game   | snooker        | monopoly | backgammon  | whist |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Flower         | daffodil | dahlia | sunflower   | balloon-flower |

