.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, doctor, pilot, freelancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the doctor##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the pilot and the person driving the roller##2
3. the police-officer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Job       | police-officer | freelancer | pilot     | doctor   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

