.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, horror, fantasy
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the person watching horror movies is between the person driving the boat and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | horror | comedy | fantasy |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

