.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, helicopter, bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person eating garlic and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Transport   | bike | snowmobile | helicopter | motorbike |

