.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, azalea, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person who growslily##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsazalea is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person who growslily and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | lily | azalea | sunflower | daisy |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

