.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, january, september
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Birthday   | june    | july  | september    | january       |

