.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, october, december
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the polish is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Birthday         | july | january | december     | october    |

