.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, singing, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, boat, trike
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person driving the tram and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing    | sudoku     | card-games | dancing |
| Transport     | jet-ski | trike | boat       | tram     |

 